DqlConstants
public class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object
implements DqlConstants

This class encapsulates the PARAMETER in DQL. The PARAMETER is the lowest level in the grammar and comtains a parameter of a particular type and the comparator for the search

Karan Gupta
